    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "half seems like a lot though if i literally had nothing. like if i just take the full dose i know i'll go low, but if i take half i might still go low. would it be safer to just skip it for tonight and catch up tomorrow? i feel like my body just needs a break from the insulin if there's no food to process.",
